{{!
    @template mod_scorecard/learner_no_items

    Empty-state notice surfaced when the scorecard has no visible items.
    Optionally renders a "manage items" affordance for callers who also
    satisfy mod/scorecard:manage.

    Context variables required:
    * body              - Lang string view:noitems_learner.
    * showmanagebutton  - Boolean; true when the affordance should render.
    * manageurl         - Absolute URL to manage.php?id=<cmid>&tab=items
                          (only required when showmanagebutton is true).
    * managelabel       - Lang string view:manageitemslink
                          (only required when showmanagebutton is true).

    Example context (json):
    {
        "body": "This scorecard isn't ready yet.",
        "showmanagebutton": true,
        "manageurl": "/mod/scorecard/manage.php?id=42&tab=items",
        "managelabel": "Add items and result bands"
    }
}}
<div class="scorecard-noitems alert alert-info">
    {{{body}}}
    {{#showmanagebutton}}
    <div class="mt-3">
        <a href="{{manageurl}}" class="btn btn-primary">{{managelabel}}</a>
    </div>
    {{/showmanagebutton}}
</div>
